      • getLanguageRefSetId

        public java.lang.String getLanguageRefSetId(IBranchPath branchPath)
        Returns with the configured language reference set ID on the given branch after checking its existence. This method falls back to existing language reference set if the configured primary one does not exist. This method never returns with null in case of empty database content, it returns with the configured primary language ID.

      • getLanguageCode

        public java.lang.String getLanguageCode()
        Returns with the abbreviation of the language code associated with the SNOMED CT language type reference set.

        E.g.:

        • en
        • en-us
        • en-gb
        • en-sg
        • en-au

        Returns:
        the abbreviation of the language code.
